      <b data-is-speakable>What Explains The COVID-19 Race Gap? : Shots - Health News</b>   <b data-is-speakable>Data shows people with certain chronic conditions are more likely to get severe COVID-19 symptoms. Why are they hit harder and what explains the disease's disproportionate affect on African Americans?</b>
