    <h3 class="slug">
        <a href="https://www.npr.org/series/812054919/the-coronavirus-crisis">The Coronavirus Crisis</a>
    </h3>
</div>
<div class="storytitle">
      <h1>Who's Hit Hardest By COVID-19? Why Obesity, Stress And Race All Matter</h1>
   <input type="hidden" id="title835563340" value="Who's Hit Hardest By COVID-19? Why Obesity, Stress And Race All Matter" />
   <input type="hidden" id="shortTitle835563340" value="Who's Hit Hardest By COVID-19? Why Obesity, Stress And Race All Matter" />
   <input type="hidden" id="modelFullUrl835563340" value="https://www.npr.org/sections/health-shots/2020/04/18/835563340/whos-hit-hardest-by-covid-19-why-obesity-stress-and-race-all-matter" />
</div>

